    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Conchoecetes artificiosus (Fabricius, 1798). NHMB-81740 (was ZMUC-CRU-3622), lectotype, female, 31.7 × 31.7 mm, Tranquebar, India, coll. I. K. Daldorff.A dorsal view (outer face right chela inset) (photograph by Peter Ng); B, dorsal view of another female 28.5 × 26.5 mm (ZMB HERBST 0819) (after Herbst 1803: pl. 58 fig. 7)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3565003/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

